org.activebpel.work.factory
Class AeDefaultWorkManagerFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.work.factory.AeDefaultWorkManagerFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeWorkManagerFactory
public class AeDefaultWorkManagerFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeWorkManagerFactory

Implements a work manager factory that looks up the CommonJ WorkManager in JNDI and constructs an IAeInputMessageWorkManager that delegates to the engine factory's process work manager.
